      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the<strong> caramelised</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and put in the oven to keep warm</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat and add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped chives</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) with a knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Cook for 30 secs or until softened</p>",
