    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>arborio rice</strong> and<strong> chopped garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the butter</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until it's evaporated</p>",
