    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1/3 of the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and stir continuously with a wooden spoon until it has absorbed</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
